QuestData.Title: Something's Amiss
QuestData.Description: The lieutenant appears to have died from severe wounds. The prince might want to hear this news.$B$BYou hear the sound of fighting coming from the market.
QuestData.LogDescription: Return to Prince Liam Greymane in the Merchant Square.
QuestData.RewardText: It's you again. Looks like you're not one to hide in the face of danger. Very well, then.
